Confidence among CEOs weakened 
in Sept. according to the Chief Executive magazine Confidence Index.  The CEO confidence index weakened to 4.88 in Sept. from 5.3
a month earlier. The index is formulated from an email survey
conducted by Chief Executive magazine.  Following is a table compiled from Chief Executive Magazine monthly
